
load ../bind
  take suit bind

load ../task
  take suit base
  take suit flow
    save suit task-flow

suit call
  link name, like term
  link bind, list bind
  link hook, mesh hook, link name

suit hook
  link name, like term
  link band, like term
  link base, list base
  link flow, list task-flow
  link task, list task

suit flow
  case call
  case save
  case back

suit save
  link road, like road

suit back
  link term, like term
